            "title": "日債遭拋售 財相出口術長息急回",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"日債遭拋售 財相出口術長息急回\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"652\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/I7S8vrUSLTI3W8XRxcwr7Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1Mg--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/a0fc3820-f725-11f0-b7e1-083cce213932\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">日債遭拋售 財相出口術長息急回</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E5%82%B5%E9%81%AD%E6%8B%8B%E5%94%AE-%E8%B2%A1%E7%9B%B8%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%A1%93%E9%95%B7%E6%81%AF%E6%80%A5%E5%9B%9E-184300147.html",
